Received the most delightful press drop last week that I’m dying to dive into. @bushwellness is a local luxury skincare brand that uses the transformative powers of CBD to make products that nourish and protect your skin. I’ve chosen the Body Butter, Body Scrub and lip balm to test out, but their collection also includes tissue oil and personal lubricant. 

I was also really excited to receive @staygoldenza spice blend, @soaringfreesuperfoods matcha powder and functional chocolate, and an @ecoffeecup.sa which is definitely going to replace the clunky ceramic travel mug I’ve been using! I also just love the journal @nickyrowbotham has put out. As a supplement to her book, ‘Finding Flow’, the journal is designed as an inspirational tool to help you unleash your untapped potential. Just the thing for a budding entrepreneur. Have you tried any of these products? If so, lemme know what you thought in the comments! 

